title: Ittibittium oryza
text:
Ittibittium oryza is a <a href="species">species</a> of <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, a marine <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Cerithiidae">Cerithiidae</a>.
Description.
The maximum recorded <a href="gastropod%20shell">shell</a> length is 3 mm.
Habitat.
Minimum recorded depth is 0 m. Maximum recorded depth is 52 m.
